OL,3,CMinister orders special review into
OL,4,CNHS trust that treated Nottingham
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FThe 32-year-old fatally attacked
OL,8,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumar before killing school
OL,10,Fcaretaker Ian Coates last June.
OL,12,FA judge handed down a hospital order
OL,13,Fat his sentencing for manslaughter by
OL,14,Fdiminished responsibility earlier this
OL,15,Fweek after the court heard he had been
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with paranoid schizophrenia.
OL,18,FThe families of the victims have
OL,19,Fquestioned the care he received before
OL,20,Fthe killings.
